Name: City Patrol
Description: Patrol city streets and maintain peace in <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Limsa Lominsa,Gridania,Ul'dah)>.

Name: Military Courier
Description: Deliver written orders to unit stationed <switch(IntegerParameter(1),at the De Nevelle Checkpoint,at the Bannock,at Sagolii Gate)>.

Name: Outskirts Patrol
Description: Patrol <switch(IntegerParameter(1),middle La Noscea,the Central Shroud,central Thanalan)> and eliminate potential threats to travelers.

Name: Beastmen Recon
Description: <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Group of kobold pickmen spotted in lower La Noscea,Ixal raiding party spotted in the South Shroud,Amalj'aa war party spotted in central Thanalan)>. Confirm presence of beastmen, and report current location. DO NOT ENGAGE.

Name: Supply Wagon Escort
Description: Escort supply wagon to <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Camp Skull Valley,Amarissaix's Spire,Camp Drybone)>. Remain alert for possible threats, and ensure supplies arrive undamaged.

Name: Pest Eradication
Description: Residents of <switch(IntegerParameter(1),middle La Noscea,the Central Shroud,central Thanalan)> request military support. Deploy to area, and cull <switch(IntegerParameter(1),goobbue,treant,giant tortoise)> population.

Name: Flagged Mission: Voidsent Elimination
Description: Cabal of minor voidsent spotted in vicinity of <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Woad Whisper Canyon,Spirithold,Nophica's Wells)>. Deploy to area and execute thorough “sweep and eliminate.”

Name: Frontline Support
Description: <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Camp Skull Valley,Eugenia's Spire,Little Ala Mhigo)> garrison requests reinforcements. Deploy to area and repel <switch(IntegerParameter(1),kobold,Ixali,Amalj'aa)> assault.

Name: Officer Escort
Description: High-ranking <switch(IntegerParameter(1),serpent,flame,storm)> officer to visit city to plan Alliance strategies. Meet said officer at airship landing, and serve as personal guard for visit duration.

Name: Border Patrol
Description: Patrol <switch(IntegerParameter(1),eastern La Noscea,the South Shroud,southern Thanalan)> and ensure major trade routes are secure.

Name: Stronghold Recon
Description: Reconnoiter the <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Kobold Dig,Ixali logging grounds,Amalj'aa encampment)> and assess enemy forces. Avoid engagements when possible, but mission completion takes priority.

Name: Search and Rescue
Description: Contact lost with unit deployed in enemy-controlled region of <switch(IntegerParameter(1),outer La Noscea,the North Shroud,northern Thanalan)>. Locate missing unit, and evacuate surviving members.

Name: Allied Maneuvers
Description: The <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Immortal Flames invite,Maelstrom invites,Order of the Twin Adder invites)> us to participate in allied maneuvers. Represent the <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Maelstrom,Order of the Twin Adder,Immortal Flames)>, and uphold our company's reputation for excellence.

Name: Flagged Mission: Crystal Recovery
Description: A joint operation is planned to prevent summoning of <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Titan,Garuda,Ifrit)> by forces entrenched in the <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Kobold Dig,Ixali logging grounds,Amalj'aa encampment)>. Cooperate with allies to infiltrate stronghold and seize cache of ritual crystals.

Name: Flagged Mission: Crystal Recovery
Description: A joint operation is planned to prevent summoning of <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Titan,Garuda,Ifrit)> by forces entrenched in the <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Kobold Dig,Ixali logging grounds,Amalj'aa encampment)>. Cooperate with allies to infiltrate stronghold and seize cache of ritual crystals.

Name: Stronghold Assault
Description: Rendezvous with Allied forces and join multi-pronged assault on <switch(IntegerParameter(1),the U'Ghamaro Mines,Natalan,Zahar'ak)>.

Name: Black Market Crackdown
Description: Plans for sale of black market weapons uncovered by intelligence. Deploy to coordinates provided, and apprehend all involved in deal.

Name: Imperial Recon
Description: Reconnoiter <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Castrum Occidens,Castrum Centri,Castrum Meridianum)> garrison and report on enemy numbers and activity.

Name: Imperial Pursuit
Description: Man described as possible imperial deserter spotted in <switch(IntegerParameter(1),eastern La Noscea,the East Shroud,northern Thanalan)>. Locate suspect and bring in for interrogation.

Name: Imperial Feint
Description: Participate in allied mobilization against imperial forces in Mor Dhona. Ensure vital feint operation succeeds.

Name: Supply Line Disruption
Description: A large-scale operation is planned to disrupt <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Sahagin supply lines in western La Noscea,Ixali supply lines in the North Shroud,Amalj'aa supply lines in southern Thanalan)>. Deploy to area, and report to commanding officer for further orders.

Name: Criminal Pursuit
Description: Dangerous criminal wanted by the <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Immortal Flames,Maelstrom,Order of the Twin Adder)> reported fleeing into <switch(IntegerParameter(1),La Noscea,the Black Shroud,Thanalan)>. Coordinate with <switch(IntegerParameter(1),flame,storm,serpent)> officer in charge of case and assist with pursuit.

Name: Supply Wagon Destruction
Description: Use imperial delivery schedule obtained by intelligence to locate and destroy Garlean supply wagon en route to <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Castrum Occidens,Castrum Centri,Castrum Meridianum)>.

Name: Chimerical Elimination
Description: <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Minotaur of exceptional size,Lamia in command of potent magicks,Chimera of unprecedented savagery)> reported in local territory. Locate creature, and ensure threat is eliminated.

Name: Primal Recon
Description: A joint operation is planned with the Scions of the Seventh Dawn to reconnoiter the <switch(IntegerParameter(1),kobold,Ixal,Amalj'aa)> for signs of summoning. Rendezvous with <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Slafswys,Dariustel,Alianne)> and do as our allies bid.

Name: Counter-magitek Exercises
Description: Training exercises are scheduled incorporating captured magitek weaponry. We are invited to participate and contribute to the development of counter-magitek tactics.

Name: Infiltrate and Rescue
Description: Civilians have been abducted by <switch(IntegerParameter(1),the Serpent Reavers,the Ixal,the Flamefangs)>. Infiltrate the enemy stronghold and liberate the captives before they are turned into thralls.

Name: Outlaw Subjugation
Description: Outlaws believed to be a splinter faction of the <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Mamool Ja,Coeurlclaws,Corpse Brigade)> have grown into an unacceptable threat. Find and summarily eliminate them.

Name: Cult Crackdown
Description: The Lambs of Dalamud are engaging in illegal recruitment in <switch(IntegerParameter(1),Limsa Lominsa,Gridania,Ul'dah)>. Under the guise of civilians, make contact with the cultists and bring their activities to light.

Name: Voidsent Elimination
Description: <switch(IntegerParameter(1),A succubus voidsent,A troubadour voidsent,The voidsent Anchag)> has been sighted nearby. Hunt down the menace before civilians can come to harm.

Name: Armor Annihilation
Description: An abandoned suit of magitek armor has run amok. Hasten to the site and coordinate with the officer in charge to destroy the machine.

Name: Invasive Testing
Description: Brazen minions of the Illuminati are field-testing weaponry on sovereign soil. Confront them and put an end to the unsanctioned experiment.

Name: Impostor Alert
Description: A brutish man has been terrorizing citizens while masquerading as a serpent sergeant. For the honor of the Alliance, locate and apprehend the impostor.

Name: Flagged Mission: Sapper Strike
Description: Intelligence reports imperial sappers in <switch(IntegerParameter(1),eastern La Noscea,the East Shroud,northern Thanalan)>, en route to destroy city fortifications. Deploy to the area, and eliminate the enemy unit.
